In this video, we break down yet another garbage job posting that’s riddled with red flags, corporate cringe, and unrealistic expectations. From laughable pay ranges that don't match the cost of living to unpaid internships doing the same work as entry-level employees, this post highlights everything wrong with today's job market. We’ll explore the shady hiring practices, the legal concerns surrounding intern compensation, and the hollow buzzwords
title: THE GARBAGE JOB TAKEOVER CONTINUES
